Package com.cafean.client.ui.util.search

Class GSTreeNode

  • java.lang.Object
    • javax.swing.tree.DefaultMutableTreeNode
      • com.cafean.client.ui.util.search.GSTreeNode
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Cloneable, javax.swing.tree.MutableTreeNode, javax.swing.tree.TreeNode
    public final class GSTreeNode
extends javax.swing.tree.DefaultMutableTreeNode
    This class represents one element in the GlobalSearchDialog results JTree. The user object controls whether this node can expand, and if so, what nodes should be added to the tree. The root node has an AbstractModel as the User Object, Direct search results have an AbstractComponent, and secondary results have either a GSViewElementLeaf or a GSReferenceElementLeaf.

      • expandNode

        public void expandNode()
        Create the children of this node in an on-demand basis. This expands the children of this node based on what object is the User object for this node. If the user object is the AbstractModel it is the root node for the tree.
